column1: "description": "Data covers monthly progress of ATMs installation at branches of Public Sector Banks (PSBs) as per Budget announcement 2013-14. It shows actual progress of 26 PSBs for reporting month and cumulative progress upto reporting month
"title": "Download XLS for Month-wise Progress Report (till 31st May 2013) of ATMs Installation at Branches of Public Sector Banks"
